OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUS probes why plane idled  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fon tarmac in a heatwave    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The US Department of Transportation is 
OL,6, investigating Delta Air Lines over     
OL,7, reports that passengers were forced to 
OL,8, wait on an idle plane in extreme heat. 
OL,10,FThe plane in question sat on the tarmac
OL,11,Fat the Las Vegas airport for at least  
OL,12,Fthree hours on Monday as temperatures  
OL,13,Frose as high as 111F (44C).            
OL,15,FMultiple passengers were seen by       
OL,16,Fmedical first responders and two people
OL,17,Fwent to a local hospital.              
OL,19,FDelta says it has offered compensation 
OL,20,Fand apologised to affected passengers. 
